OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F339A1783685999
OL,3,COrganised gangs thought to be behind
OL,4,Chuge flytip
OL,6,FOrganised crime gangs operating on a
OL,7,F"commercial scale" are thought to be
OL,8,Fbehind a huge flytip in Bradford, the
OL,9,Fcity council has said.
OL,11,FThousands of tons of household and
OL,12,Fcommercial rubbish was found dumped on
OL,13,Fland running alongside Midland Road,
OL,14,Fnear Bradford City's Valley Parade
OL,15,Fstadium, after reports were first made
OL,16,Fon 1 July.
OL,18,FPictures from the scene show piles of
OL,19,Fwaste stretching about 100m either
OL,20,Fside of a wide track accessible to
OL,21,Fvehicles.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/5
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,340,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F339A1783685999
OL,3,COrganised gangs thought to be behind
OL,4,Chuge flytip
OL,6,FBradford Council's executive member
OL,7,Ffor neighbourhoods Cllr Ian Walker
OL,8,Fsaid: "This is organised criminality
OL,9,Foperating on a commercial scale.
OL,11,F"As such, the site is a crime scene
OL,12,Fand will need to be investigated to
OL,13,Fgather evidence and determine the
OL,14,Fnature of waste materials. Any risks
OL,15,Fwill need to be identified and
OL,16,Fmitigated before any further action
OL,17,Fcan be taken. There is not currently a
OL,18,Fclear timetable of how long this will
OL,19,Ftake."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/5
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,340,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F339A1783685999
OL,3,COrganised gangs thought to be behind
OL,4,Chuge flytip
OL,6,FHe added: "Any incident of fly tipping
OL,7,Fis disrespectful and damaging to the
OL,8,Flocal community and the environment.
OL,9,FIllegal waste dumping on this scale is
OL,10,Funforgivable, and we will work with
OL,11,Fpartners to ensure that those
OL,12,Fresponsible are held to account."
OL,14,FIn a joint statement, Manningham's
OL,15,Findependent councillors, Muhammed Ali
OL,16,FIslam, Muhammad Haseeb Khan and
OL,17,FMohammed Saliss, said they were
OL,18,F"deeply appalled".
OL,26,@nD@KOUtD@aO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/5
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,340,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F339A1783685999
OL,3,COrganised gangs thought to be behind
OL,4,Chuge flytip
OL,6,F"This is completely unacceptable and
OL,7,Frepresents a blatant disregard for our
OL,8,Fcommunity and the environment.
OL,10,F"Manningham is a proud and vibrant
OL,11,Fward at the heart of Bradford.
OL,13,F"We will not tolerate anyone treating
OL,14,Four community as a dumping ground."
OL,16,FThe Environment Agency is now
OL,17,Finvestigating and said it was trying
OL,18,Fto trace the landowner to secure the
OL,19,Fsite.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/5
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
