CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F339A1783685999
OL,3,COrganised gangs thought to be behind
OL,4,Chuge flytip
OL,6,FArea environment manager Ben Hocking
OL,7,Fsaid: "We are assessing the site's
OL,8,Fenvironmental impact and making
OL,9,Fenquiries to trace the landowner to
OL,10,Fensure the site is secured.
OL,12,F"Waste crime scars communities and...
OL,13,Fwe're acting quickly to tackle illegal
OL,14,Factivity and shut down sites."
